    {
      "id": "PopularPost80651",
      "post_content": "I run this with [mindlock orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mindlock orb) also as a shut down, but I add in [intruder alarm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=intruder alarm) to shut down their creatures too, and then start stockpiling eon counters on [Magosi, the Waterveil](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magosi, the Waterveil) so that even if they can somehow break the combo, I have an extra turn stored to put it back into place. It's an overly complicated combo, but life-draining stasis is worth it.",
