      "id": "PopularPost102375",
      "post_content": "Try combining it with Teferi's Puzzlebox. :D Try it in a Black/Red deck so what you can have a grip of instant burn when it's your time to lose your hand. Your opponent loses theirs first, though. This is particularly true if you run out Teferi's Puzzlebox and then Maralen. Also- if they do just tutor to destroy your Maralen (which sort of makes her a 3 cost Timewalk that does 3 damage to your opponent, anyway) then the Puzzlebox will mean it is just a matter of time before you draw another copy of her. Clunky, but fun!",
