    {
      "id": "PopularPost129331",
      "post_content": "This card makes the **best** mono black EDH general. Sure, she lets your opponents set up their lategame plans (which *can* be dangerous, especially in EDH). That's why no one kills her for the first few turns. And in those turns, you search for [Necropotence](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence) and then [Venser's Journal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Venser's Journal) / [Ivory Tower](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ivory Tower) (I personally prefer the journal because it uncaps your handsize and provides better life gain than the tower, but sometimes you need to drop a life gain on turn 4, in which case the journal's hefty mana cost can become a problem, so put both in for optimal strategizing).\n  \nThe thing that makes her perfect for an EDH general is that you don't have to wait to pull her from your 100 card deck. You play her 3rd turn from the command zone. Once she`s in play, you don`t need to pull anything else from your 100 card deck, the rest falls into place however you see fit.\n  \nOf course the [Necropotence](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence) may turn you ... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "BloodJunkie",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost129331\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">This card makes the <b>best</b> mono black EDH general. Sure, she lets your opponents set up their lategame plans (which <i>can</i> be dangerous, especially in EDH). That's why no one kills her for the first few turns. And in those turns, you search for <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Necropotence\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence\">Necropotence</a> and then <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Venser's Journal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Venser's Journal\">Venser's Journal</a> / <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ivory Tower\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ivory Tower\">Ivory Tower</a> (I personally prefer the journal because it uncaps your handsize and provides better life gain than the tower, but sometimes you need to drop a life gain on turn 4, in which case the journal's hefty mana cost can become a problem, so put both in for optimal strategizing).\r<br/>The thing that makes her perfect for an EDH general is that you don't have to wait to pull her from your 100 card deck. You play her 3rd turn from the command zone. Once she`s in play, you don`t need to pull anything else from your 100 card deck, the rest falls into place however you see fit.\r<br/>Of course the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Necropotence\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Necropotence\">Necropotence</a> may turn you ... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 129331)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '129331'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy52348\">BloodJunkie</span>\r\n                                (1/18/2011 11:53:02 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
